author: More Perfect Union
description:
Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies have lost $1 trillion in value over the last month. It's bad news for a notoriously volatile—and unregulated—crypto sector.

Trump has pledged to make the U.S. the "crypto capital of the world" and dismantled oversight and rolled back safety regulations on the industry.

ft. @kaburbank
title: Everything wrong with the crypto industry explained

author: More Perfect Union
description:
Turkey prices are up 36% this year. Ham? A whopping 49% more expensive than last year. And even pie crust is 13% more expensive, according to a recent study by Groundwork, AFT, and The Century Foundation.

We broke down what's behind the rising price-tag on your Thanksgiving dinner.
title: Trump is using a Walmart promotion to gaslight you about Thanksgiving prices

author: More Perfect Union
description: Why did Trump back down on Swiss tariffs? The Swiss government, and many others, are figuring out that the best way to secure a great trade deal has nothing to do with negotiating - it's by bribing and flattering Donald Trump.
title: What Trump’s Tariffs Are REALLY About
